These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-1::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, singing, video-games
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person who's hobby is singing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |
| Hobby   | collecting | video-games | singing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-2::.
There 3 different types of food: cranberry, pumpkin, cherry
1. the person eating cranberry is between the person eating pumpkin and the person eating cherry##2
2. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3    |
| Food   | cherry | cranberry | pumpkin |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-3::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  architect, analyst, entrepreneur
1. the analyst is between the architect and the entrepreneur##2
2. the analyst is on the left of the architect##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |  2   |    3    |
| Job   | entrepreneur | analyst | architect |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-4::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, august, february
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
2. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person who's birthday is in august and the person who's birthday is in september##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2   |     3      |
| Birthday   | september | february | august |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-5::.
3 different pets are kept: cat, mouse, lizard
1. the owner of the cat is between the owner of the lizard and the owner of the mouse##2
2. the owner of the lizard is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Pet   | mouse | cat | lizard |

 #################################

 
